<p><q>Thanks. I will,</q> I said.</p>

<p><q>So anyway, how's the job hunt going?</q></p>

<p><q>Nothing yet. To tell you the truth, I haven't been looking very hard. Kumiko's working, and I'm taking care of the house, and we're managing for now.</q></p>

