<p><q>Something bad?</q></p>

<p><q>Something very, very bad,</q> Creta Kano prophesied-in a small but penetrating voice, like the prophet bird that lived in the forest.</p>

<h2>15</h2>

<h2>The Only Bad Thing That Ever Happened in May Kasahara's House</h2>

<h2>•</h2>

<h2>May Kasahara on the Gooshy Source of Heat</h2>

